TunableVariant.description:
If enabled and an amount is awarded, displays a dialog to the user.

The notification will have access to the amount awarded as a 
localization token. e.g. {0.GalacticCredits}

If enabled, this notification will display when this interest payment is made.
Token 0 is the Sim - i.e. {0.SimFirstName}
Token 1 is the interest payment amount - i.e. {1.Money}
